Description of tadpoles. Descriptive statistics for 17 morphological characters were based on 66 tadpoles at developmental stages 25, 27, 36 and 38 (
Table 4
). The following detailed description is based on a sample of 5 tadpoles from the same lot (INPA-H 32983 , original field number
APL 13031
), collected from a single clutch and reared to stage 37 before preservation.
